name: The Sleeping Citadel
description:
The Sleeping Citadel is considered by many as the dreamer capital of the Tapestry.
Countless dreamers meet within its walls to share their experiences, trade knowledge and artifacts or simply look for partners for their next expedition.
Many of them consider it a safe haven and refuse to leave, fearing the dangers that roam outside.
The wise, however, know that when it comes to the Tapestry, no place is truly safe.
